### SHAP Analysis — Why the Model Predicts What It Does

**SHAP (SHapley Additive exPlanations)** decomposes each prediction into individual feature contributions. Based on game theory — each feature is a "player" and SHAP calculates its marginal contribution.

**SHAP Beeswarm Plot:**
- Each dot = one patient
- X-axis = SHAP value (positive → pushes prediction toward HD, negative → pushes toward healthy)
- Color = feature value (red = high, blue = low)

