## 🚀 Phase 6: Deployment & Real-Time Prediction

**Goal:** Save models & build real-time prediction.

### Models Saved
- `logistic_regression_model.pkl` — Champion model
- `random_forest_model.pkl` — For SHAP explainability
- `xgboost_model.pkl` — Gradient boosted alternative
- `voting_ensemble_model.pkl` — LR + RF + SVM soft voting
- `standard_scaler.pkl` — Feature scaler
- `feature_names.json` — Feature ordering

### Voting Ensemble (LR + RF + SVM)

**Soft voting:** Averages the predicted probabilities from all 3 models.

$$P_{ensemble} = \frac{P_{LR} + P_{RF} + P_{SVM}}{3}$$

- **AUC: 0.940** (highest of all models!)
- But LR alone still wins on accuracy (89.1% vs 87.0%)
- Trade-off: Ensemble is better at ranking risk, LR is better at hard classification

